Generic single-database configuration for Alembic.

## Usage

### Create a new migration

```bash
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "description of changes"
```

### Apply migrations

```bash
# Upgrade to latest
alembic upgrade head

# Upgrade one version
alembic upgrade +1

# Downgrade one version
alembic downgrade -1
```

### View migration history

```bash
alembic history
alembic current
```

### Initial Setup

The initial migration has been created with all models:
- User
- Subscription
- Payment
- UsageMetric
- KeywordSearch
- Opportunity

To apply the initial migration:

```bash
alembic upgrade head
```
